tests.name: equilateral - all sides are equal
tests.test_code:
begin
  TapAssertTrue(Self, 'equilateral - all sides are equal', true, PartialFail.equilateral(2, 2, 2));

tests.name: equilateral - sides may be floats
tests.test_code:
begin
  TapAssertTrue(Self, 'equilateral - sides may be floats', true, PartialFail.equilateral(0.5, 0.5, 0.5));

tests.name: isosceles - last two sides are equal
tests.test_code:
begin
  TapAssertTrue(Self, 'isosceles - last two sides are equal', true, PartialFail.isosceles(3, 4, 4));

tests.name: isosceles - first two sides are equal
tests.test_code:
begin
  TapAssertTrue(Self, 'isosceles - first two sides are equal', true, PartialFail.isosceles(4, 4, 3));

tests.name: isosceles - first and last sides are equal
tests.test_code:
begin
  TapAssertTrue(Self, 'isosceles - first and last sides are equal', true, PartialFail.isosceles(4, 3, 4));

tests.name: isosceles - equilateral triangles are also isosceles
tests.test_code:
begin
  TapAssertTrue(Self, 'isosceles - equilateral triangles are also isosceles', true, PartialFail.isosceles(4, 4, 4));

tests.name: isosceles - sides may be floats
tests.test_code:
begin
  TapAssertTrue(Self, 'isosceles - sides may be floats', true, PartialFail.isosceles(0.5, 0.4, 0.5));

tests.name: scalene - no sides are equal
tests.test_code:
begin
  TapAssertTrue(Self, 'scalene - no sides are equal', true, PartialFail.scalene(5, 4, 6));

tests.name: scalene - sides may be floats
tests.test_code:
begin
  TapAssertTrue(Self, 'scalene - sides may be floats', true, PartialFail.scalene(0.5, 0.4, 0.6));
